pro_desc: This project is done for the sole purpose of Integrating ML with the Web. This is an Image classification on Browser with Tensorflow Js and node js where we could see the predictions of an image on the screen to which class(className) it belongs and how much(probability).

Amazon Price Tracker, built with Selenium and Python, scrapes the Amazon India website to find all the products that match your requirements and generates a JSON report out of it. Being not as fast as scrapy, it reduces the chances of getting tracked and blocked by Amazon.
